  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nFork choice is throwing errors when we shutdown a client and start again from the same database.\r\n\r\nThis is likely because we do not serialize and store the fork choice store on shutdown (and restore it on startup).\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nStore the fork choice in the `persist` method (if this is too slow, consider only storing it when the beacon chain gets dropped:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/3d559d8b4149b94db612520998a97876ac0a4c00/beacon_node/beacon_chain/src/beacon_chain.rs#L236-L252\r\n\r\nEnsure the fork choice loads gracefully here:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/3d559d8b4149b94db612520998a97876ac0a4c00/beacon_node/beacon_chain/src/beacon_chain.rs#L187-L234",
